/* MEDIA QUERIES */

/* For Tablets */
@media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .first-sect {
        width: 90%;
        height: 300px;
    }
    .nav-list {
        padding-left: 40px;
        padding-right: 40px;
    }
    .sign-up {
        width: 120px;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
    .sect-img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
    }
    .red-form input,
    .red-form button {
        width: 90%;
        margin: 10px 0;
    }
}

/* For Mobile (Phone Sizes) */
@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .first-sect {
        width: 100%;
        height: 250px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .nav-bar {
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    .nav-list {
        flex-direction: column;
        padding-left: 0;
        padding-right: 0;
    }
    .Navlink {
        padding: 15px 20px;
    }
    .sect-img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
    }
    .form-div {
        padding: 10px;
    }
    .sign-up {
        width: 100px;
    }
    .red-form input {
        width: 80%;
    }
}

/* For Small Mobile Devices */
@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
    .first-sect {
        width: 100%;
        height: 200px;
    }
    .nav-bar {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .nav-list {
        display: block;
        padding-left: 0;
    }
    .Login-btn {
        font-size: 14px;
    }
    .sect-img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
    }
    .form-div {
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .red-form input {
        width: 100%;
    }
}
```

### Key Changes:
- **Media Queries**: Added at breakpoints for tablets (`max-width: 1024px`), mobile (`max-width: 768px`), and small phones (`max-width: 480px`).
- **Nav Menu**: Adjusts for mobile screens, making the navigation stack vertically and spacing elements more comfortably.
- **Image Scaling**: Ensures that images fit within the container and scale appropriately on different screen sizes.
- **Layout Adjustments**: Reduced padding and adjusted the layout of sections (e.g., form fields) to fit smaller screens.

This updated code ensures that your website's layout remains user-friendly and accessible across various screen sizes, from desktop to mobile devices.




